title: Sheryl (Sheryl Crow doc)
description:
It's Tig and Cheryl... and Sheryl!... as our intrepid doc duo take on a brand new Sheryl Crow documentary. Does it make them happy? Are they strong enough? Can Cheryl sing "Soak Up The Sun" as well as Sheryl can? You'll have to listen to find out! *this episode spills beans* Get merch at podswag.com/truestory (tigandcheryltruestory@gmail.com)
